{"tid":1662432,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[風水救港] 1020局勢預測","createTime":"2019-10-18T18:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T09:52:25.000Z","uid":39858,"like":120,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"84ac00f4be2c193bb934818d8765724141d5d367","tid":1662432,"uid":39858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:14:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O4B2s7W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO4B2s7W.png&h=5c5dca95&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n2019年10月20日<br />\n己亥年九月廿二日<br />\n通勝 宜: <span style=\"color: red;\">補捉</span><br />\n<br />\n庚甲己<br />\n寅戌亥<br />\n<br />\n天干:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">甲庚相沖</span><br />\n甲己合土<br />\n地支:<br />\n寅亥合<br />\n<br />\n飛星:<br />\n6 2 4<br />\n5 <span style=\"color: red;\">7 </span>9<br />\n1 3 8<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">七赤破軍賊星入囚</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">預測:<br />\n大眾市民依舊響應呼籲 外出遊行表達訴求<br />\n但黑警於該日有大型拘補行動<span style=\"color: red;\">(不是驅散!)</span><br />\n黑警與示威人士展開沖突<br />\n示威人士不敵黑警大量送頭</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">趨吉避凶:<br />\n和理非人士在遊行過後 宜及早和平有序散去<br />\n勇武手足盡可化身和理非一天<br />\n特別注意東方 南方 北方 切勿於這三方與黑警有正面衝突<br />\n祝各位平安回家<br />\n1020 13:00 見</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/UD6tRGX.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n五行抗暴<br />\n水德為首<br />\n五大訢求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"79edbc65cebaa8a7e37bae46abf7bf8686e08bea","tid":1662432,"uid":248536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:16:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4faa35480de7e3ea747912e74b2ec2b93132b8","tid":1662432,"uid":12169,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:17:09.000Z","msg":"西方姐係邊度..."},{"pid":"fae23cbe83a22afb4c7576a8c62d88dccb893d2