<strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n<br />\n[i]<strong>醫療、教育方向</strong>[i]<br />\n<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"d829bf97642259afb7e9ed76dd0995b56dda6e67","tid":1662432,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T21:02:17.000Z","msg":"雖不信，但結論合理"},{"pid":"b02e3a29fbc7a15148166a624912660038ef5ca4","tid":1662432,"uid":314462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T21:44:59.000Z","msg":"亞巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e282a02c873c8dd69a4f571fa601d67a20e965","tid":1662432,"uid":247184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T22:44:25.000Z","msg":"破軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368096df458a88b99ae1978112ebb627e0d1e770","tid":1662432,"uid":194363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T23:44:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&lsquo;&rsquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975b1690eeaf8c8521cbd6ee7a7da3ca1c1fb3a6","tid":1662432,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T23:47:27.000Z","msg":"in 新巴 we trust <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6c5ea58cf379d034409f4f4c411083ada65988a","tid":1662432,"uid":263367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:20:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"06cfe38eaf0785460c737702d7001cc1440ae320","tid":1662432,"uid":254114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc